== 製作 ==
=== 發展和劇本洩漏 ===
[[File:LACMA_The_Hateful_Eight_Live_Reading.jpg|right]]
2013年11月，導演昆汀·塔倫提諾表示正在計劃新作品，是一部西部電影。他說，這將不會是《[[決殺令|決殺令]]》的續集<ref name=Nextfilm>{{cite web|title=Tarantino Reveals Plans For Next Movie|url=http://tv.yahoo.com/nighttime/tarantino-reveals-plans-next-movie-091643390.html|publisher=Yahoo: Nighttime in No Time|accessdate=2013-11-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131130014257/http://tv.yahoo.com/nighttime/tarantino-reveals-plans-next-movie-091643390.html|archivedate=2013-11-30}}</ref>。2014年1月12日，據透露，這部電影命名為《八惡人》（''The Hateful Eight''）。電影有望在2014年的夏天開始製作，但在2014年1月劇本遭到流出，震怒的塔倫提諾決定取消這部電影和打算重寫一份新的劇本來替代<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.moviethatmatters.com/quentin-tarantino-plans-to-axe-hateful-eight-after-the-script-leaked/|title=Quentin Tarantino Plans to drop 'Hateful Eight' after the Script Leaked|date=2014-01-22|accessdate=2014-08-29|publisher=Movies that Matter|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140130054554/http://www.moviethatmatters.com/quentin-tarantino-plans-to-axe-hateful-eight-after-the-script-leaked/|archivedate=2014-01-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming Jr.|first=Mike|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/01/quentin-tarantino-hateful-eight-leak-novel/|title=Quentin Tarantino Shelves 'The Hateful Eight' After Betrayal Results In Script Leak|date=2014-01-21|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2014-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808000317/http://www.deadline.com/2014/01/quentin-tarantino-hateful-eight-leak-novel/|archive-date=2014-08-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他自稱是將劇本給了幾位值得信賴的同事帶回去看，其中包括[[布魯斯·鄧恩|布魯斯·鄧恩]]、[[提姆·羅斯|提姆·羅斯]]與[[麥可·馬德森|麥可·馬德森]]，但究竟是誰洩漏劇本就不得而知<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/quentin-tarantino-sues-gawker-over-hateful-eight-script-leak-1.2513071 | publisher=CBC News | title=Quentin Tarantino sues Gawker over Hateful Eight script leak | date=2014-01-21 | accessdate=2014-08-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203144922/http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/quentin-tarantino-sues-gawker-over-hateful-eight-script-leak-1.2513071 | archive-date=2014-02-03 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Gettell|first1=Oliver|title=Quentin Tarantino mothballs 'Hateful Eight' after script leak|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-quentin-tarantino-hateful-eight-postponed-script-leak-20140122-story.html|date=2014-01-22|website=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6fAK60XaO?url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-quentin-tarantino-hateful-eight-postponed-script-leak-20140122-story.html|archive-date=2016-02-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

4月19日，塔倫提諾在{{link-en|洛杉磯王牌酒店|Ace Hotel Los Angeles}}的美國藝術家劇院現場讀出被洩露的劇本。本次活動於[[洛杉磯郡藝術博物館|洛杉磯郡藝術博物館]]的電影獨立會舉辦，電影評論家{{link-en|艾爾維斯·米切爾|Elvis Mitchell}}亦有出席<ref name=LACMA_Live_Reading>{{citation|title=World Premiere of a Staged Reading by Quentin Tarantino: The Hateful Eight|url=http://www.lacma.org/event/staged-reading-quentin-tarantino|date=2014-04-19|accessdate=2014-08-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427130408/http://www.lacma.org/event/staged-reading-quentin-tarantino|archivedate=2014-04-27}}</ref>。塔倫提諾解釋說，他們將會遵循劇本的第一稿來拍電影，他補充說，他還另外寫了兩個不同結局的新草稿。加入塔倫提諾劇組的演員包括[[山繆·傑克森|山繆·傑克森]]、[[寇特·羅素|寇特·羅素]]、[[安柏·譚柏林|安柏·譚柏林]]、{{link-en|詹姆士·帕克斯|James Parks (actor)}}、[[華頓·哥金斯|華頓·哥金斯]]、{{link-en|柔伊·貝爾|Zoë Bell}}、[[詹姆斯·瑞馬|詹姆斯·瑞馬]]、丹娜·格瑞爾和在劇本流出前的麥可·馬德森、提姆·羅斯與布魯斯·鄧恩<ref name=Tarantino_Live_Read>{{cite web|last=Anderton|first=Ethan|title=Tarantino's 'Hateful Eight' Live-Read Reveals Script Still Developing|url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2014/tarantinos-hateful-eight-live-read-reveals-script-still-developing/|accessdate=2014-01-27|work=FirstShowing.net|date=2014-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424045517/http://www.firstshowing.net/2014/tarantinos-hateful-eight-live-read-reveals-script-still-developing/|archive-date=2014-04-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

於2014年5月28日，已冷靜的塔倫提諾說，《八惡人》將於[[懷俄明州|懷俄明州]]開始進行拍攝，並有望於2015年推出<ref>{{cite web|last1=Seddon|first1=Gem|title=Quentin Tarantino's The Hateful Eight Lands Full Cast, Will Shoot In November|url=http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/quentin-tarantinos-the-hateful-eight-full-cast-shoot-november/|website=wegotthiscovered.com|accessdate=2014-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140616012741/http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/quentin-tarantinos-the-hateful-eight-full-cast-shoot-november/|archive-date=2014-06-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Friedman|first1=Roger|title=Exclusive: Tarantino Movie "Hateful Eight" Has November Start Date|url=http://www.showbiz411.com/2014/05/24/exclusive-tarantino-movie-hateful-eight-has-november-start-date?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=exclusive-tarantino-movie-hateful-eight-has-november-start-date|website=showbiz411.com|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606203026/http://www.showbiz411.com/2014/05/24/exclusive-tarantino-movie-hateful-eight-has-november-start-date?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=exclusive-tarantino-movie-hateful-eight-has-november-start-date|archive-date=2014-06-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2014年的[[聖地亞哥國際動漫展|聖地亞哥國際動漫展]]上塔倫提諾終於證實了這部電影，並表示他正在為電影寫出第三份劇本稿<ref>{{cite news|last1=Stedman|first1=Alex|title=Quentin Tarantino Confirms He’s Still Doing ‘The Hateful Eight’|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/quentin-tarantino-is-still-doing-the-hateful-eight-1201269958/|accessdate=2014-07-28|work=Variety|date=2014-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728151757/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/quentin-tarantino-is-still-doing-the-hateful-eight-1201269958/|archive-date=2014-07-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 選角 ===
