essdate=2014-11-10|publisher=deadline.com|date=2014-11-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6fAKHeM4u?url=http://deadline.com/2014/11/channing-tatum-hateful-eight-quentin-tarantino-movie-1201274888/|archive-date=2016-02-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來在同一天，溫斯坦影業釋出了一份明確的新聞稿，其中包括[[山繆·傑克森|山繆·傑克森]]、[[寇特·羅素|寇特·羅素]]、[[珍妮佛·傑森·李|珍妮佛·傑森·李]]、[[華頓·哥金斯|華頓·哥金斯]]、[[德米安·畢契爾|德米安·畢契爾]]、[[提姆·羅斯|提姆·羅斯]]、[[麥可·馬德森|麥可·馬德森]]和[[布魯斯·鄧恩|布魯斯·鄧恩]]都將出演本片。而塔圖的加入也被證實<ref name=NovemberPress>{{cite news|last1=Ramisetti|first1=Kirthana|title='The Hateful Eight' cast announced: Samuel L. Jackson, Jennifer Jason Leigh and Channing Tatum among all-star cast in Quentin Tarantino's latest film|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/hateful-cast-announced-article-1.2001806|accessdate=2014-11-09|publisher=nydailynews.com|date=2014-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108134349/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/hateful-cast-announced-article-1.2001806|archive-date=2014-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來在2015年1月23日，TWC宣布了全體的演員，另外包括{{link-en|詹姆士·帕克斯|James Parks (actor)}}、丹娜·格瑞爾、{{link-en|柔伊·貝爾|Zoë Bell}}、{{link-en|吉因·瓊斯|Gene Jones (actor)}}、基斯·傑佛遜、{{link-en|李·霍斯利|Lee Horsley}}、克雷格·史塔克與貝琳達·歐音諾的加入<ref>{{cite news|title=Filming Starts for Quentin Tarantino’s The Hateful Eight|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/402527-filming-starts-for-quentin-tarantinos-the-hateful-eight|accessdate=2015-01-23|publisher=comingsoon.net|date=2015-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150123200847/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/402527-filming-starts-for-quentin-tarantinos-the-hateful-eight|archive-date=2015-01-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 攝製 ===
原定的拍攝行程從2014年11月延至2015年初開拍<ref>{{cite news|title=Quentin Tarantino's The Hateful Eight shoot moved back to 2015|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/showbiz/489271/Quentin-Tarantino-s-The-Hateful-Eight-shoot-moved-back-to-2015|accessdate=2014-07-17|work=[[Daily_Express|Daily Express]]|date=2014-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140717022420/http://www.express.co.uk/news/showbiz/489271/Quentin-Tarantino-s-The-Hateful-Eight-shoot-moved-back-to-2015|archive-date=2014-07-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="RightsTWC" />。2014年9月26日，《{{link-en|丹佛郵報|The Denver Post}}》報導，[[科羅拉多州|科羅拉多州]]贊助了500萬美元的製作資金，並宣布電影完全會在{{link-en|科羅拉多州西南部|Southwest Colorado}}取景拍攝<ref name=denverpost>{{cite news|last1=Kennedy|first1=Lisa|last2=Svaldi|first2=Aldo|title=Quentin Tarantino set to shoot "Hateful Eight" in Colorado|url=http://www.denverpost.com/entertainment/ci_26611060/quentin-tarantino-set-shoot-hateful-eight-colorado|accessdate=2014-09-27|publisher=denverpost.com|date=2014-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303172741/http://www.denverpost.com/entertainment/ci_26611060/quentin-tarantino-set-shoot-hateful-eight-colorado|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。那裡的900英畝的牧場也將作為拍攝地。10月16日，該縣的規劃委員會開會申請臨時建起的建築的使用的許可證<ref name="denverpost" />。據傳，主要拍攝於2014年12月8日開始，在美國科羅拉多州的施密德牧場附近的[[特柳賴德|特柳賴德]]進行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://emertainmentmonthly.com/2014/11/19/quentin-tarantino-follow-hateful-eight-shoot-70mm/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-07-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150715183618/http://emertainmentmonthly.com/2014/11/19/quentin-tarantino-follow-hateful-eight-shoot-70mm/ |archivedate=2015-07-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-12814-james-bond-pic-spectre-hateful-eight-start-shooting-vin-diesel-wraps-last-witch-hunter/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-12-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160514160944/http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-12814-james-bond-pic-spectre-hateful-eight-start-shooting-vin-diesel-wraps-last-witch-hunter/ |archivedate=2016-05-14 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Dyer|first1=Kyle|title=New Tarantino movie starts filming near Telluride|url=http://www.9news.com/story/entertainment/2014/12/10/hateful-eight-telluride-tarantino/20203055/|accessdate=2014-12-11|publisher=9news.com|date=2014-12-10|archive-date=2014-12-11|archive-url=https://archive.is/20141211025101/http://www.9news.com/story/entertainment/2014/12/10/hateful-eight-telluride-tarantino/20203055/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但後來於2015年1月23日，溫斯坦影業才正式宣布拍攝開始<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Quentin Tarantino Starts Shooting ‘Hateful Eight’|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/quentin-tarantino-starts-shooting-hateful-eight-1201413017/|accessdate=2015-01-24|publisher=variety.com|date=2015-01-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6fAJvPHGi?url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/quentin-tarantino-starts-shooting-hateful-eight-1201413017/|archive-date=2016-02-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 吉他事件 ====
片中[[珍妮佛·傑森·李|珍妮佛·傑森·李]]被[[寇特·羅素|寇特·羅素]]毀損的吉他為馬丁吉他博物館所收藏的1870年代的[[馬丁吉他|馬丁吉他]]真品，並非原先的預計使用的複製品。在片中[[珍妮佛·傑森·李|珍妮佛·傑森·李]]知道那把吉他為真品，而[[寇特·羅素|寇特·羅素]]並不知曉，所以每個人在現場中對於吉他被摧毀表示「非常驚訝」，而李的反應是真實的。博物館館長Dick Boak說，博物館沒有被告知該劇本包括吉他被打碎的場景，該博物館宣稱吉他已無法修復，雖然這把價值約4萬美金的吉他有購買保險，但博物館方面仍對此感到相當不滿。由於這次事件，博物館將不再借出吉他給電影的製作。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://reverb.com/news/cf-martin-responds-to-the-destruction-of-145-year-old-guitar-on-hateful-eight-set |title = Martin Responds to 'Hateful Eight' Destruction of Antique Six String |author = Chris McMahon |date = 2016-02-04 |publisher = Reverb.com |language = en |access-date = 2017-02-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170222053647/https://reverb.com/news/cf-martin-responds-to-the-destruction-of-145-year-old-guitar-on-hateful-eight-set |archive-date = 2017-02-22 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 拍攝 ===
由曾與塔倫提諾合作過《[[追殺比爾|追殺比爾]]》、《[[惡棍特工|惡棍特工]]》和《[[決殺令|決殺令]]》的攝影師[[羅伯特·理察森|羅伯特·理察森]]負責，並以{{link-en|Ultra Panavision 70|Ultra Panavision 70}}來完成本片的{{link-en|70釐米電影|70 mm film}}，這和1992年的《[[遠離家園|遠離家園]]》的70釐米相當<ref name=cinemablend>{{cite news|last1=Pucho|first1=Kristy|title=Quentin Tarantino's Hateful Eight To Be Widest 70mm Release In 20 Years|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Quentin-Tarantino-Hateful-Eight-Widest-70mm-Release-20-Years-67031.html|accessdate=2014-12-10|publisher=cinemablend.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224043022/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Quentin-Tarantino-Hateful-Eight-Widest-70mm-Release-20-Years-67031.html|archive-date=2014-12-24|dead-url=no}}{{full|date=July 2015}}</ref>。電影使用了[[Panavision|Panavision]]的{{link-en|變形鏡頭|Anamorphic format}}和2.75：1的[[長寬比_(影像)|長寬比]]。過去於1950至1960年代，曾使用此超廣角長寬比的電影如《[[賓漢|賓漢]]》（1959年）、《[[叛艦喋血記_(1962年電影)|叛艦喋血記]]》（1962年）與《{{link-en|瘋狂世界 (1963年電影)|It's a Mad, Mad, Mad, Mad World|瘋狂世界}}》（1963年）<ref name=RopeSiliconMay2015>{{cite news|last1=Brevet|first1=Brad|title=More Pictures from Quentin Tarantino's 'Hateful Eight' as First Trailer Screens for Cannes Crowd|date=2015-05-14|url=http://www.ropeofsilicon.com/more-pictures-from-quentin-tarantinos-hateful-eight-as-first-trailer-screens-for-cannes-crowd/|accessdate=2015-06-30|publisher=ropeofsilicon.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725103549/http://www.ropeofsilicon.com/more-pictures-from-quentin-tarantinos-hateful-eight-as-first-trailer-screens-for-cannes-crowd/|archive-date=2015-07-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 音樂 ==
2015年，塔倫提諾在[[聖地牙哥國際動漫展|聖地牙哥國際動漫展]]上宣布，[[顏尼歐·莫利克奈|顏尼歐·莫利克奈]]將為電影作曲；這是莫利克奈繼1975年的《{{link-en|一個天才、兩個朋友和一個傻子|A Genius, Two Partners and a Dupe}}》後相隔40年再度幫西部片配樂<ref name="Comic Con">{{cite news |last=Lincoln |first=Ross A. |title=Quentin Tarantino Delivers Mind-Blowing Look At ‘Hateful Eight’ – Comic Con |url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/hateful-eight-comic-con-first-look-panel-quentin-tarantino-1201474348/ |date=2015-07-11 |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline]] |accessdate=2015-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150712121411/http://deadline.com/2015/07/hateful-eight-comic-con-first-look-panel-quentin-tarantino-1201474348/ |archive-date=2015-07-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Johnston |first=Raymond |title=Tarantino and Morricone settle the score in Prague |url=http://www.praguepost.com/cinema/48900-tarantino-and-morricone-scoring-in-prague |date=2015-07-19 |work=[[The_Prague_Post|The Prague Post]] |accessdate=2015-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150720162751/http://praguepost.com/cinema/48900-tarantino-and-morricone-scoring-in-prague |archive-date=2015-07-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 市場行銷 ==
塔倫提諾出席了2014年的[[聖地亞哥國際動漫展|聖地亞哥國際動漫展]]，來向大眾證實電影將開始製作。2014年7月30日，電影的前導海報釋出<ref>{{cite news|last1=Billington|first1=Alex|title=Tarantino's New Western 'The Hateful Eight' Unveils Another Poster|url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2014/tarantinos-new-western-the-hateful-eight-unveils-another-poster/|accessdate=2014-08-01|work=FirstShowing.net|date=2014-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140802032344/http://www.firstshowing.net/2014/tarantinos-new-western-the-hateful-eight-unveils-another-poster/|archive-date=2014-08-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月14日，{{link-en|斜線電影公司|/Film}}證實1分40秒的前導預告將隨著於8月22日上映的《[[萬惡城市2：紅顏奪命|萬惡城市2：紅顏奪命]]》一同放映<ref>{{cite news|last1=Fischer|first1=Russ|title=Quentin Tarantino’s ‘The Hateful Eight’ Trailer Debuts With ‘Sin City 2,’ Will Not Be Online|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/hateful-eight-trailer-release/|accessdate=2014-08-14|publisher=slashfilm.com|date=2014-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140816201533/http://www.slashfilm.com/hateful-eight-trailer-release/|archive-date=2014-08-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
2014年9月3日，[[溫斯坦影業|溫斯坦影業]]定於2015年秋季在全球市場發布<ref name=RightsTWC>{{cite news|title=Weinsteins Will Distribute Quentin Tarantino’s ‘Hateful Eight’ Worldwide|url=http://deadline.com/2014/09/weinsteins-get-global-distibution-of-tarantinos-hateful-eight-828282/|accessdate=2014-09-03|publisher=deadline.com|date=2014-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905102134/http://deadline.com/2014/09/weinsteins-get-global-distibution-of-tarantinos-hateful-eight-828282/|archive-date=2014-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年2月9日，TWC將負責全球發布的工作，但需要塔倫提諾親自批准<ref>{{cite news|last1=Roxborough|first1=Scott|title=Berlin: Quentin Tarantino Personally Approving Buyers of 'Hateful Eight'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/berlin-quentin-tarantino-personally-approving-771749|accessdate=2015-02-11|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2015-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211090924/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/berlin-quentin-tarantino-personally-approving-771749|archive-date=2015-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年6月26日，宣布導演及演員將出席2015年7月11日的[[聖地亞哥國際動漫展|聖地亞哥國際動漫展]]，同時也提到70釐米的放映及相關消息<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hipes|first1=Patrick|title=‘Hateful Eight’ Going To Comic-Con: Western Heads South With Tarantino & Cast|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/hateful-eight-comic-con-2015-quentin-tarantino-cast-1201458713/|accessdate=2015-06-27|work=deadline.com|date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627111656/http://deadline.com/2015/06/hateful-eight-comic-con-2015-quentin-tarantino-cast-1201458713/|archive-date=2015-06-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《八惡人》獲得了一致好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據327篇專業影評持有75%的新鮮度，平均得分7.5／10；該網站共識：「《八惡人》提供了另一種很好鎖定的動作目標，結合了[[昆汀·塔倫提諾|昆汀·塔倫提諾]]的招牌幽默和頂級暴力，同時也展現了他對電影製作更強力的掌控」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hateful_eight/ |title=The Hateful Eight reviews |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151214011817/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hateful_eight/ |archive-date=2015-12-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分68，代表「普遍好評」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-hateful-eight |title=The Hateful Eight (2015) |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151219062042/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-hateful-eight |archive-date=2015-12-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[IGN|IGN]]評論家吉姆·韋沃達給了本片9.5分，並認為這部電影是「塔倫提諾最好的電影，也是2015年最好的之一」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/12/16/the-hateful-eight-review|title=The Hateful Eight Review|publisher=IGN|author=Jim Vejvoda|date=2015-12-16|accessdate=2015-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151219124145/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/12/16/the-hateful-eight-review|archive-date=2015-12-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

